*xosd-2.2.5-r1 (29 Jan 2004)

  29 Jan 2004; Nick Hadaway <raker@gentoo.org> xosd-2.2.5-r1.ebuild:
  Added xinerama to IUSE.  Properly set configure options for the xmms
  plugin.  Delete the "no" directory if created.  See bug #39800.

  10 Dec 2003; Heinrich Wendel <lanius@gentoo.org> xosd-2.2.5.ebuild:
  stable on x86

*xosd-2.2.5 (29 Sep 2003)

